Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:27.81,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\alpha&33&\b0\fs20\c&H1F211D&\fax-0.03\pos(678.858,491.715)\frz19.95}Som v lietadle do Oshimi!\N Čoskoro sa stretneme!\N Teším sa na to\N ako si spolu pohovoríme!
