Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-chan, my letíme!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj, ako to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh áno, Akane-chan sme naozaj vysoko!
